Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you have premonition dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,People are talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought those dreams might cause some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The dreams are probably something to do with mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The mushi living inside your dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're responsible for showing you those premonitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And they will multiply more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You should control their numbers with this medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How often do you have those dreams right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,One or two out of ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon it will become at least four or five.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when you should take this medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take any more than that, it will be toxic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you don't take it at all, you will be unable to awaken from your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's important is the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you take the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I will come again around the time the medicine runs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...sweet dreams...
