Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Do not converse with one talking in their sleep."{i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those are the words from the land of Utopia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't even been a year since I last came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,mushi-shi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I had something I wanted to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw what happened to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you guessed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a water vein!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1434)}We can expand our rice paddies with this water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We hit water!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one of Jin's dreams came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Go tell the others in the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is from the farmers to thank us. \NThey gave us this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I sort of feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't put good food on the table just by doing blade sharpening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm grateful for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Bayberries!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But Jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of your dreams coming true has increased...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,just like that mushi-shi said it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That mushi are showing me \Nthe dreams and things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if... just what if what he's saying is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You will? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The cliff on the westside crumbled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for your prediction, we'd be goners.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I get scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever one of my dreams comes true,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but feel as if I caused it to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,These are to thank you for the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have a good dream for us, too, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask for the impossible. It's just a dream, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, we'll be looking forward to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you were given those\N premonitions to help others...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,after all, everyone seems happy because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I told my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still felt apprehensive about\N my premonition dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and I started taking the medicine willingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She was at the seashore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I never had a dream about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he not foresee a calamity like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because I took this medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I couldn't save Mayu's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped taking the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, right after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,more and more of my premonition\N dreams started to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone left a thank you gift in front of our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to... cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're drenched in sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't feel well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't because of a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the exact same disease I had seen in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A green mold would start at the fingertips...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and spread through the body, \Nmaking it crumble like dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the only one left in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You said your name was Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When that dream came true,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to the realization that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...when you visited the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you had deceived me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's inside me isn't mushi that would show me premonition dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're mushi that bring my dreams\N out to infect the real world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That green mold disease...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It started spreading to those who were near me first...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then my neighbors...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,then the plots across the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And right before my very eyes, the exact scene in my dream played out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All the things that I had predicted before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...were events that were created in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you lie to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,your ties with the mushi cannot \Nbe completely severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it becomes a parasite in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,all you can do is live with it in balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I were to tell you \Nthe true nature of this mushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't be able to handle \Nthe magnitude of your creations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I should've died from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I caused these disasters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you let me live?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's come to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything I can to find a way\N to cut you off from the mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:44.71,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\frz349.8\c&H222F3A&\3c&H222F3A&\pos(681.334,413.333)\1a&H11&}Imeno{\c&H243B48&\3c&H243B48&} no {\c&H203A4A&\3c&H203A4A&}Awai
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Imeno no Awai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This mushi normally live in the host's dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but come out of the dreams on occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When they come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,they become the medium to make the dream the host was having infect reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the mushi don't make all your dreams into premonition dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:13:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but the more they multiply, the more often they come out of your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And their ability to turn your dreams into reality grows both in range and in scale as well. {change}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But these mushi themselves are very weak in that they will disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,if exposed to sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unknown why they want to\N come out into our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's said that there's a pathway connecting dreams and reality through which only mushi can traverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And while the host is awake, \Nthat's where the mushi sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can find that pathway,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might be able to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I've never seen or heard of a case before of such a fast pace and a big scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That medicine alone can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And if I increase the dosage...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You took all the medicine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get the antidote!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.16,Alt,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...living anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see his eyes moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's started to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's talking in his sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The fault does not lie with the mushi either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You were both just carrying on with life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't done anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those wild geese I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So he is talking in his sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not coherent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just where are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry back to reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a field of reeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He answered me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this ringing in my ears?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Our conversation just now linked his dream to reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So he sees these as wild geese?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a flock of {\i1}Imeno no Awai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You must hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:17:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've... killed you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something is showing up on the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that my dream being reflected on the screen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fire in my dream has spread through the pillow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's fire here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get water!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dream came into reality through my pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A pathway only for the mushi to traverse...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While the host is awake, that's where the mushi sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's where you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You damned... mushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...did I get cut, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he got good first aid treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he'll manage to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know it would turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All I did was cut the pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said that the word "makura" comes\N from "tamashii no kura".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40\bord2.5\fad(50,50)\i1}Note :- Makura = pillow; Tamashii no kura = soul storage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For almost one-third of your life, \Nyour pillow cradles your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that's why it is believed that the pillow where soul dwells.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The pillow is also the nest for the {\i1}Imeno no Awai,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and is also the pathway that connects dreams to reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought if you cut it, you had be\N the one who'd lose something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Between dreams and reality lies "soul storage".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unless one takes this path,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he cannot go see the land of Utopia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thereafter, I heard that the man started working as a blade sharpener again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was well-known for his skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But for whatever reason, \Nhe gradually became disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times, he would wave \Na sword around in the streets,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and at the end, finally stabbed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People said...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that he was very afraid to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He thought if he went to sleep, \Nhis soul would slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'd not dreamed once...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...since the day he cut his pillow.
